                  Arthur Schnitzler</addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">IX. Sternwartestrasse 1</rs>.</addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb41240">Autriche</rs></addrLine></address></div>
